cat << EOF
The PhotoClip is a simple image viewer and editor mostly designed
for digital camera pictures.
The goal is to make a program that can be conveniently used
as both viewer and editor at the same time.

For now the only editing feature is recomposition, i.e. cropping
and rescaling of image.
EOF
